title: Cheap Trick - The Forum LA(Deluxe 2-CD) 1979 ak320
description:
Cheap Trick - The Forum LA(Deluxe 2-CD) 1979 ak320

This started off as just the one CD of Live at the LA  Forum But It got a few Bonus Tracks.   and then more and finally it became a Bootleggers Transmission Impossible. Once ya start you just cant stop LOL.

 In April 2016, the band was inducted into the Rock and Roll Hall of Fame.
Hey same class as Steve Miller was in. LOL

Current members

    Robin Zander – lead vocals, rhythm guitar, keyboards (1974–present)
    Rick Nielsen – lead guitar, keyboards, backing vocals (1974–present)
    Tom Petersson – bass, backing vocals (1974–1980, 1987–present)
    Daxx Nielsen – drums (2010–present)

    Jon Brant – bass, backing vocals (1981–1987, 2004–2005, 2007; one-off 1999)
